# PHP Reference

## Naming
```php
function skel_function_name() { }  // Prefix: skel_
$variable_name = 'value';
__( 'Text', 'skel' );              // Domain: 'skel'
```

## Formatting
```php
if ( $condition ) { }              // Spaces inside parentheses
function_call( $arg1, $arg2 );     // Tabs for indentation
```

## Escape/Sanitize
```php
echo esc_html( $text );            echo esc_attr( $attr );
echo esc_url( $url );              echo wp_kses_post( $html );
sanitize_text_field( $_POST['f'] );  sanitize_email( $_POST['e'] );  absint( $_GET['id'] );
```

## Loop & Parts
```php
<?php if ( have_posts() ) : while ( have_posts() ) : the_post(); ?>
	<article <?php post_class(); ?>><?php the_title( '<h2>', '</h2>' ); the_content(); ?></article>
<?php endwhile; endif; ?>

get_template_part( 'template-parts/content', get_post_type() );
get_template_part( 'template-parts/card', 'product', [ 'product_id' => $id ] );
```
